# Summary
This documentation describes the integration between Osano (a data privacy platform) and Amplitude, explaining how Osano discovers and classifies personal data in Amplitude to support compliance with privacy laws like GDPR and CCPA, and how to set up the connection using Amplitude's API key and Secret Key.

